des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Danby Air Conditioner. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps: 
(1) Download our “Danby Smart Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Danby Smart Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Danby Smart Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Danby Smart Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Danby Smart Home” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Air conditioner.”
“Alexa, turn off the Air conditioner.”
“Alexa, set the Temperature to XX degrees.”
“Alexa, set the Fan to low.”
“Alexa, set the Fan to Med.”
"Alexa, set the Fan to High."
